Employee Handbook - 2024 Edition
 Welcome to the company! This handbook outlines the policies, procedures, and expectations for all
 employees.
 Casual Leave Policy:- Employees are entitled to 12 days of casual leave per calendar year.- Leave requests should be submitted via the HR portal at least 3 days in advance.
 Working Hours:- Standard working hours are from 9:00 AM to 5:30 PM, Monday to Friday.- Remote work is permitted with manager approval.
 Contact:
 For HR-related queries, please contact hr@company.com.
